data.description: Ranch home newly updated, new roof that sits on almost 1/2 acre lot that is fenced.  On main level there is a nice size living room with an eat in kitchen, includes near new appliances, 2 large bedrooms with plenty of closet space and a full bathroom.  Downstairs you will find the laundry room with washer and dryer that can stay if you wish.  Downstairs there is plenty of room for another bedroom and kids playroom, TV room, etc.  Backyard is spectacular with a covered patio for outside dining.  Great neighborhood.
